snippet.title: Detective Conan Runner: Gameplay
snippet.description:
“Detective Conan Runner: Race to the Truth” is a horizontal runner mobile game based on the hit Japanese animation series "Detective Conan". Join the adorable Conan and his friends as they run, overcome obstacles, and collect points to chase down suspects!

▪ Official Facebook account: https://www.facebook.com/conanrunnerEN
▪ Official Twitter account: https://twitter.com/conanrunner_en
▪ Official Instagram account: https://www.instagram.com/conanrunner_en

▪ Official Website (for United States, United Kingdom, Canada, Australia, Netherlands, New
Zealand, Denmark, Finland, Russia, Sweden): https://caseclosed-en.bushiroad.com

▪ Official Website (for Hong Kong, Taiwan, South Korea, Singapore, Thailand, Malaysia,
Germany, Chile, Mexico, Switzerland, Saudi Arabia, Vietnam, France, Indonesia, Philippines,
Spain, Brazil, Egypt, Italy, Norway): https://detectiveconan-en.bushiroad.com/
